---
import '../styles/sections/manifesto.css';
---

<section id="manifesto" class="manifesto relative py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="manifesto-title">
  <!-- Hero Image -->
  <figure class="manifesto__hero-image absolute inset-0 opacity-10" data-animate="fade-in">
    <img
      src="/images/bg-manifesto.jpg"
      alt="Ambiente de consulta humanizada"
      loading="eager"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
    <div class="manifesto__hero-overlay absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/80 to-white/60"></div>
  </figure>

  <div class="manifesto__backdrop" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="manifesto__photo" role="presentation"></div>
    <!-- Opção 1: Grid geométrico (ativo por padrão) -->
    <svg class="manifesto__pattern" viewBox="0 0 1440 900" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="grid-pattern" x="0" y="0" width="80" height="80" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <rect x="0" y="0" width="80" height="80" fill="none" stroke="rgba(31,62,70,0.18)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="3" fill="rgba(125,168,123,0.25)"/>
        </pattern>
        <radialGradient id="fade-edges" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="70%">
          <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:rgba(255,255,255,0);stop-opacity:1" />
          <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:rgba(250,250,248,0.3);stop-opacity:1" />
        </radialGradient>
      </defs>

      <rect class="manifesto__pattern-grid" width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid-pattern)"/>
      <rect class="manifesto__pattern-fade" width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#fade-edges)"/>
    </svg>

    <svg class="manifesto__orbits" viewBox="0 0 800 800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <g class="manifesto__orbit manifesto__orbit--one" fill="none" stroke="rgba(31,62,70,0.28)" stroke-width="1.2">
        <circle cx="400" cy="400" r="240" />
      </g>
      <g class="manifesto__orbit manifesto__orbit--two" fill="none" stroke="rgba(125,168,123,0.24)" stroke-width="1.6">
        <circle cx="400" cy="400" r="310" />
      </g>
      <g class="manifesto__nodes" fill="rgba(31,62,70,0.55)">
        <circle cx="640" cy="280" r="5" />
        <circle cx="530" cy="580" r="4" />
        <circle cx="320" cy="180" r="3" />
      </g>
    </svg>

    <span class="manifesto__grain"></span>
  </div>

  <div class="manifesto__content container relative z-10">
    <div class="manifesto__intro max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 id="manifesto-title" class="manifesto__title text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        Quando o cuidado deixa de ser automático.
      </h2>
      <p class="manifesto__lead text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Sustento consultas longas, olho para padrões e reescrevo o plano junto com você. Abaixo, um resumo de como isso acontece na prática.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto__matrix max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <header class="manifesto__matrix-header grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8 text-center" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Quando é automático</span>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-petrol uppercase tracking-wider">Quando fazemos juntos</span>
      </header>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="manifesto__row group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-sage/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-normal" data-row>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="manifesto__index flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-sage/20 to-accent-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-sage font-bold text-sm">01</span>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 flex-1">
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--soft text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                Protocolos prontos, pouca escuta.
              </p>
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--bold text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
                Escuta longa e leitura de padrões antes de qualquer decisão.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__row group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-petrol/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-normal" data-row>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="manifesto__index flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-petrol/20 to-accent-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-petrol font-bold text-sm">02</span>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 flex-1">
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--soft text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                Consulta curta, foco na prescrição.
              </p>
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--bold text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
                Sessões de 120 minutos para cruzar história, dados e rotina.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__row group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-gold/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-normal" data-row>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="manifesto__index flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-gold/20 to-accent-gold/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-gold font-bold text-sm">03</span>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 flex-1">
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--soft text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                Tecnologia afasta o médico.
              </p>
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--bold text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
                Uso IA apenas para organizar informação e dedicar presença total.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="manifesto__row group p-6 rounded-xl bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-200 hover:border-accent-sage/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-normal" data-row>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="manifesto__index flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-sage/20 to-accent-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-sage font-bold text-sm">04</span>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 flex-1">
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--soft text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                Plano rígido, sem ajustes.
              </p>
              <p class="manifesto__col manifesto__col--bold text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
                Mapa vivo com ajustes contínuos e acordos compartilhados.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
